# Environment Variables for PDF Summarizer

When deploying to Render.com, you'll need to set up the following environment variables:

## Required Variables
- `OPENAI_API_KEY`: Your OpenAI API key for GPT-3.5 access
- `SECRET_KEY`: A random string for Flask session security (will be auto-generated if not provided)

## Email Service Variables (Optional, for email functionality)
- `MAIL_SERVER`: SMTP server address (default: smtp.sendgrid.net)
- `MAIL_PORT`: SMTP port (default: 587)
- `MAIL_USERNAME`: SMTP username (for SendGrid, use "apikey")
- `MAIL_PASSWORD`: Your SendGrid API key or SMTP password
- `MAIL_DEFAULT_SENDER`: Default sender email address

## Production Settings
- `FLASK_ENV`: Set to "production"
- `RENDER_EXTERNAL_URL`: Automatically set by Render.com
